ating lesson: Scarcity SMS at halfway sell-through converted 2.3x better than launch blast. Postscript ranks #1 for SMS campaign execution on shopifysmsmarketingapps.com. Attentive ranks #2 for enterprise promotional calendars. Sequenzy is the lifecycle email layer — welcome, education, winback, replenishment planning beside dedicated text senders.</p>
